{"prompt": "Create an inviting website for a handmade jewelry designer. The layout should feature a delicate lavender purple.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Enchanted Adornments</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #e6d9f7; /* Delicate Lavender Purple */\n            color: #4a3767; /* Deeper shade of purple for contrast */\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #d0bde7; /* Slightly darker lavender for header */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: 300;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-style: italic;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .gallery {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n        .gallery-item {\n            flex-basis: calc(33.333% - 20px);\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #f5f0fc; /* Very light lavender */\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .gallery-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .gallery-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 2px solid #d0bde7;\n        }\n        .gallery-item h3 {\n            margin: 0 0 5px 0;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            color: #4a3767;\n        }\n        .gallery-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #6a5a8a;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            background-color: #d0bde7;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .gallery-item {\n                flex-basis: calc(50% - 20px);\n            }\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .gallery-item {\n                flex-basis: 100%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Enchanted Adornments</h1>\n        <p>Handcrafted Jewelry with a Touch of Magic</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Collections</h2>\n        <div class=\"gallery\">\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/d0bde7/ffffff?text=Amethyst+Dream\" alt=\"Amethyst Necklace\">\n                <h3>Amethyst Dream</h3>\n                <p>Ethereal necklaces featuring genuine amethyst stones.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/d0bde7/ffffff?text=Rose+Quartz+Glow\" alt=\"Rose Quartz Earrings\">\n                <h3>Rose Quartz Glow</h3>\n                <p>Delicate earrings designed to bring warmth and love.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/d0bde7/ffffff?text=Moonstone+Whispers\" alt=\"Moonstone Bracelet\">\n                <h3>Moonstone Whispers</h3>\n                <p>Intricate bracelets inspired by the magic of the moon.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/d0bde7/ffffff?text=Pearl+Lace\" alt=\"Pearl Ring\">\n                <h3>Pearl Lace</h3>\n                <p>Elegant rings with lustrous pearls and fine craftsmanship.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/d0bde7/ffffff?text=Crystal+Sparkle\" alt=\"Crystal Pendant\">\n                <h3>Crystal Sparkle</h3>\n                <p>Dazzling pendants that catch the light beautifully.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/d0bde7/ffffff?text=Garnet+Fire\" alt=\"Garnet Brooch\">\n                <h3>Garnet Fire</h3>\n                <p>Bold brooches for a statement of unique style.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Enchanted Adornments. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}